track_notes: This is the first of 2 tracks covering Mt Despair, The Razor and The Viking as this is usually an overnight hike camping at Viking Saddle. It picks up Mt Despair and The Razor on the way, but note that the detour to The Razor adds about 2.5 hours to the walk due to the bush bashing needed. The second track is associated with The Viking summit.
track_title: Camp Creek to Viking Saddle via Mt Despair and The Razor
